schema.name: Q1
schema.sql: SELECT DayOfWeek, count(*) AS c FROM default.ontime WHERE Year >= 2000 AND Year <= 2008 GROUP BY DayOfWeek ORDER BY c DESC;

schema.name: Q2
schema.sql: SELECT DayOfWeek, count(*) AS c FROM default.ontime WHERE DepDelay>10 AND Year >= 2000 AND Year <= 2008 GROUP BY DayOfWeek ORDER BY c DESC;

schema.name: Q3
schema.sql: SELECT Origin, count(*) AS c FROM default.ontime WHERE DepDelay>10 AND Year >= 2000 AND Year <= 2008 GROUP BY Origin ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;

schema.name: Q4
schema.sql: SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, count() FROM default.ontime WHERE DepDelay>10 AND Year = 2007 GROUP BY Carrier ORDER BY count() DESC;

schema.name: Q5
schema.sql: SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, avg(cast(DepDelay>10 as Int8))*1000 AS c3 FROM default.ontime WHERE Year=2007 GROUP BY Carrier ORDER BY c3 DESC

schema.name: Q5-JOIN
schema.sql: SELECT Carrier, c, c2, c*100/c2 as c3 FROM( SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, count(*) AS c FROM ontime WHERE DepDelay>10 AND Year=2007 GROUP BY Carrier) q JOIN ( SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, count(*) AS c2 FROM ontime WHERE Year=2007 GROUP BY Carrier ) qq USING (Carrier) ORDER BY c3 DESC;

schema.name: Q6
schema.sql: SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, avg(cast(DepDelay>10 as Int8))*1000 AS c3 FROM default.ontime WHERE Year>=2000 AND Year <=2008 GROUP BY Carrier ORDER BY c3 DESC;

schema.name: Q6-JOIN
schema.sql: SELECT Carrier, c, c2, c*100/c2 as c3 FROM( SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, count(*) AS c FROM ontime WHERE DepDelay>10 AND Year>=2000 AND Year<=2008 GROUP BY Carrier) q JOIN ( SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, count(*) AS c2 FROM ontime WHERE Year>=2000 AND Year<=2008 GROUP BY Carrier ) qq USING (Carrier) ORDER BY c3 DESC;

schema.name: Q7
schema.sql: SELECT IATA_CODE_Reporting_Airline AS Carrier, avg(DepDelay) * 1000 AS c3 FROM default.ontime WHERE Year >= 2000 AND Year <= 2008 GROUP BY Carrier;

schema.name: Q7-JOIN
schema.sql: SELECT Year, c1/c2 FROM( select Year, count(*)*100 as c1 from ontime WHERE DepDelay>10 GROUP BY Year) q JOIN ( select Year, count(*) as c2 from ontime GROUP BY Year ) qq USING (Year) ORDER BY Year;

schema.name: Q8
schema.sql: SELECT Year, avg(DepDelay) FROM default.ontime GROUP BY Year;

schema.name: Q9
schema.sql: SELECT Year, count(*) as c1 FROM default.ontime GROUP BY Year;

schema.name: Q11
schema.sql: SELECT avg(c1) FROM (SELECT Year,Month,count(*) AS c1 FROM default.ontime GROUP BY Year,Month) a;

schema.name: Q12
schema.sql: SELECT OriginCityName, DestCityName, count(*) AS c FROM default.ontime GROUP BY OriginCityName, DestCityName ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;

schema.name: Q13
schema.sql: SELECT OriginCityName, count(*) AS c FROM default.ontime GROUP BY OriginCityName ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10
